# LaTeX build artifacts (regenerated by build.sh)
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.bbl
*.blg
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.synctex.gz
*.toc
mainNotes.bib
supplementNotes.bib

# main.pdf and supplement.pdf are intentionally TRACKED so the
# advisor / reviewer / GitHub-link readers see the rendered paper
# without having to install a TeX distribution. Run `bash build.sh`
# and `bash build_supplement.sh` after .tex edits and commit the
# refreshed PDFs alongside the source.
